00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,440
[Baiyang] He's hitting the net again.

24
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,840
Baiyang!

25
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:11,800
[Baiyang breathes heavily]

26
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,120
