27
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,560
[scoffs]

28
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,320
We are alike.

29
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,200
I like to play under pressure.

30
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,200
What should we do?

31
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,920
Baiyang seems to be wounded.

32
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:32,760
[Coach Qi] Baiyang, come
and treat your wound.

33
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:36,160
You use the snake-ball

34
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,280
too often.

35
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,960
It drains your energy faster.

36
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,240
In certain circumstances,

37
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,280
you must be flexible.

38
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:44,920
I don't think so.

39
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,640
I should catch every single ball.

40
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,640
This should be okay, Coach.

41
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,400
I can feel your determination

42
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,320
in your strategy.

43
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,200
I like it.

44
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:06,720
Oh. Thank you.

45
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,000
So...

46
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:10,760
I will definitely use my own way

47
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:11,800
to defeat you.

48
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,920
[Jian] This is just what I have
been expecting.

49
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,200
[Yan Zhiming] He is really stubborn.

50
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:20,040
[tense music]

51
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,400
[Jian] What a strong momentum.

52
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,920
There is great pressure. I like it.

53
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,880
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

54
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,400
[Baiyang] This is my way of playing!

55
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:36,880
[whooshes]

56
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:41,320
-[both grunting]
-[thwacking]

57
00:03:43,080 --> 00:03:44,160
Kui Jian has been caught up.

58
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:49,720
This guy seems to have been
wound up again.

59
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,200
In this case,

60
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,440
Kui Jian won't let the ball touch the net.

61
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,160
To be honest,
I really don't want to compete with him.

62
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:58,960
He is terrifying.

63
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:06,400
-[both grunting]
-[thwacking]

64
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,240
[umpire 1] The match is over.

65
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,320
Baiyang from Yu Qing won

66
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,680
with a score of seven to five.

67
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:20,360
[audience applauds]

68
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:23,480
[umpire 1] Yu Qing defeated Di Liu High
School with a score of seven to five.

69
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:25,399
Yu Qing entered the top four of winners.

70
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:28,560
[light music]

71
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,440
[Baiyang sighs]

72
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,960
[exhales sharply]

73
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,200
-[Xiuwen] We won.
-[Huang Jing] Great.

74
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,160
We won.

75
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,880
-Baiyang is so great.
-Bravo.

76
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,000
How are you?

77
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,560
You were messing with it.

78
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,760
Sorry, Coach.

79
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,600
[audience cheering]

80
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,760
-[Baiyang grunts]
-[Dayong] Be careful.

81
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,680
Baiyang, good job.

82
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,240
Thank you.

83
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:07,360
[Lu Xia] Baiyang finally found his own way
of playing tennis.

84
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,320
Baiyang, are you okay?

85
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:12,440
Don't worry, I am fine.

86
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,200
Go and treat your wound.

87
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:16,320
You really think your head
is harder than iron.

88
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:18,520
I don't care whether it was hard or not.

89
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,440
I won anyway.

90
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,160
Okay, you are right about everything.

91
00:05:23,520 --> 00:05:25,320
Your bandana is dirty
and may get you infected.

92
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,760
It won't be dirtier than you.

93
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:28,720
You...

94
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,760
[Coach Qi sighs]

95
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,680
I will help him.

96
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,800
Take off your bandana.

97
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,640
[groans]

98
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:52,880
[Yan Zhiming] Don't move.

99
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,120
Yan.

100
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:02,520
I still insisted on my own
way of playing tennis.

101
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,960
[somber music]

102
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:08,920
Come on, hold it.

103
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,640
[groans]

104
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:15,480
You are right.

105
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,320
Strategies are always just strategies.

106
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,840
They won't become habits,

107
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,800
and won't become part of you.

108
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,080
[cheering]

109
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,320
[Coach Muyun laughs]

110
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:31,160
[Di Liu Team] ♪ I spin and jump
with eyes closed ♪

111
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:34,280
-♪ the dust cannot be seen ♪
-They seem to have won the match.

112
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,760
-[Di Liu Team] ♪ Are you indulged yet? ♪
-[Coach Muyun laughs]

113
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:39,200
[cheering, laughing]

114
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:42,000
[Coach Muyun] Kui Jian, come here.

115
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,720
-Mr. Six.
-Go and see what's wrong with him.

116
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,840
-Okay.
-Hurry up.

117
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,320
-Mr. Six, let's sing together.
-[Coach Muyun] I am coming.

118
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,360
Are you okay?

119
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:58,040
Oh. Okay.

120
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:01,400
You are really a tough man.
The girls must like you even more.

121
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,600
Uh...

122
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,000
Thank you.

123
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,320
You really scared me just now.

124
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:07,040
I worship those who play desperately.

125
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,640
Having a match against you

126
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,800
really broadened my view.

127
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,200
Oh. I know you.

128
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,520
You are Yu Qing's strategist.

129
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,240
Mm-hmm. Kind of.

130
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,960
Your rackets are really special.

131
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,960
I'll make one for you if you like.

132
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,400
[Jian] I can't make one
as well as Mr. Six though.

133
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,880
But holding this racket makes me relaxed.

134
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:30,480
Thank you.

135
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:33,040
-We also witnessed Mr. Six's way.
-[distant cheering]

136
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,440
Indeed, the simpler the strategies are

137
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,960
the more efficient they will be.

138
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:40,240
We didn't even learn the
basic techniques of Mr. Six.

139
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,480
But he told us, "Happiness is
the most important thing."

140
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:43,720
[soft chuckle]

141
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,600
You didn't play today.

142
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,560
I missed the chance to play
with you before.

143
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:57,360
It is a pity. We must have a match
if there is a chance in the future.

144
00:07:57,640 --> 00:07:59,080
There must be a chance in the future.

145
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:01,320
Come on, guys. Good luck
in your following matches.

146
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,440
[cheering]

147
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:11,840
[Lu Xia] They are still so happy
even though they lost.

148
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:22,800
TENNIS PARK

149
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,040
[Ye] Captain.

150
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,600
[Jingtian shushes]

151
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,240
[playful music]

152
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,240
Captain. What is this?

153
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,000
It contains

154
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:40,159
rich vitamin C and vitamin B

155
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,240
and is made from quality fish,
green peppers,

156
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,640
carrots, lemons, and apples.

157
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:46,600
There are 49 types of ingredients
in total. It took effort--

158
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,840
Stop. So what's your point?

159
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,960
It can help us become stronger.

160
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:54,160
-[gasps]
-Will we become stronger if we drink it?

161
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,520
You have watched the matches of Yu Qing.

162
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:59,000
They were really good in the match.

163
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,760
That's because they drink Yan-juice.

164
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:03,400
Ahh. I understand.

165
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:05,880
But why do we have to hide here?

166
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,960
Dahai.

167
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,200
We can't let others discover

168
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,520
such a precious thing.

169
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:10,960
Ah.

170
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:12,680
Captain, can we drink it now?

171
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:15,280
[comical music]

172
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,760
I will drink it first.

173
00:09:19,920 --> 00:09:21,160
Leave some for us.

174
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,280
[Dahai] That's enough.

175
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:27,480
[gurgles]

176
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:39,080
Eh. Where is my Yan-juice?

177
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,640
[man on P.A.] Urgent announcement.

178
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,760
Team members of Ying Cai High School

179
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,800
will be absent from matches
due to food poisoning.

180
00:09:45,040 --> 00:09:46,680
Competitors,

181
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,280
please pay attention to food safety.

182
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,400
Urgent announcement.

183
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:53,320
Team members of Ying Cai High School...

184
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:57,560
[crickets chirping]

185
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:14,040
[TV playing]

186
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,880
[door opens]

187
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:34,600
[Lu Xia] I am back.

188
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,520
[Xiangqian] Why did you stop practicing?

189
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,600
Is it because of the noise here?
Did I bother you?

190
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,560
No.

191
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:48,600
Are you hungry?
I ordered your favorite pizza.

192
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,480
There's no need.

193
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:53,040
[TV playing]

194
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:54,840
[Coach Muyun] Keep trying,

195
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:56,480
and you will get to taste

196
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,160
a different kind of flavor.

197
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:01,360
[Coach Muyun] Drinks have no right
or wrong.

198
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:05,440
You don't have to stick
with the old or the new,

199
00:11:05,800 --> 00:11:08,320
victory or failure.

200
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:12,360
What's up? Do you have anything to say?

201
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:15,280
[somber music]

202
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,720
[stutters]

203
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,680
I will go and have a shower.

204
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,280
Eh.

205
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,160
[birds chirping]

206
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,480
[Tang Jiale sighs]

207
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,200
I am so hungry.

208
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:37,240
Why hasn't Lu Xia come?

209
00:11:37,480 --> 00:11:39,480
What's taking him so long?

210
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,280
[sighs]

211
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:44,560
[Qiao Chen] He is coming.

212
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,720
[grunts]

213
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:53,040
After the match, we were all told to be
here at this time. Why are you late again?

214
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,880
That's right, and you are so late.

215
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,720
We were almost about to leave without you.

216
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:58,480
I'm only a few minutes late.

217
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:02,360
Actually, you're
31 minutes 36 seconds late.

218
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,400
[Yan Zhiming] It's still too early

219
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:06,720
to make a prediction
of the match result now.

220
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:09,840
But we already missed opportunities
to gather information about the opponents.

221
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:12,960
Okay. Let's go right now.

222
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,160
Xing Yao and Yu Cen
have begun their match.

223
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:17,640
If our next opponent is Xing Yao,

224
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:20,800
this match is a good chance to get
to know our opponent.

225
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:25,520
Ying, I heard that the cheering squad
of Xing Yao is wonderful.

226
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:27,640
Today, we can take a look for ourselves.

227
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:30,440
It seems we will have a strong
opponent soon.

228
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,880
Hmm.

229
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:34,400
Wonderful. We can finally compete
with Xing Yao.

230
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,320
Mmm.

231
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:36,600
This day has come at last.

232
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,560
After we defeat Xing Yao,

233
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,000
we can enter the national final.

234
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:44,120
[crowd cheering in distance]
Xing Yao, come on!

235
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:47,320
-Xing Yao, come on!
-Let's go and watch Xing Yao's match.

236
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,560
-[Peng] Let's go.
-[Ying] Okay.

237
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:59,560
NATIONAL SENIOR HIGH TENNIS LEAGUE

238
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:02,520
JI JINGWU, XINGYAO HIGH SCHOOL
VERSUS MENG YUE, YU CEN HIGH SCHOOL

239
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,000
[whooshes, thwacks]

240
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:09,200
[tense music]

241
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:12,600
[sighs]

242
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:16,000
If I knew it was such a weak opponent,
I wouldn't have wasted my time on him.

243
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:20,400
[breathing heavily]

244
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:26,560
[tense music]

245
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,920
Isn't it just the beginning of the match?

246
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:34,000
But Xing Yao has already overwhelmed
the opponents. They are really strong.

247
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:35,760
[crowd cheering]
Xing Yao!

248
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:37,560
Xing Yao! Xing Yao!

249
00:13:38,400 --> 00:13:39,600
[grunts]

250
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,600
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

251
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:45,080
[audience applauds]

252
00:13:45,160 --> 00:13:47,200
[audience cheering]
Xing Yao!

253
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,920
[audience cheering continues]
Xing Yao!

254
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:58,440
[action music]

255
00:14:06,280 --> 00:14:08,000
[audience cheering]
Xing Yao!

256
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:14,520
Xing Yao's cheering squad is huge.

257
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,960
It is like a music concert.

258
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:18,440
We must be well prepared.

259
00:14:18,520 --> 00:14:20,080
-We can't lose the momentum.
-Mmm.

260
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:22,040
Does he consider himself as a star?

261
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,320
In this match,

262
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:24,920
he is the star.

263
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:27,520
He really looks forward to
competing with our Captain.

264
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:30,600
Our Captain will defeat him
in the future matches anyway.

265
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,120
[audience cheering]
Xing Yao!

266
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:34,080
