00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:16,520
can't demonstrate their full power
in the match,

543
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:18,720
it will be very bad

544
00:30:19,280 --> 00:30:20,320
for Yu Qing.

545
00:30:21,320 --> 00:30:22,280
Give me some time.

546
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:23,600
I will be back on track.

547
00:30:24,520 --> 00:30:26,200
I am giving you the time.

548
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,320
We have our training plan for the team.

549
00:30:29,320 --> 00:30:30,960
But what you need most

550
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,160
is the time for yourself.

551
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:35,480
I am not saying

552
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:37,760
you should stop training and rest at home.

553
00:30:38,240 --> 00:30:39,800
[exhales sharply]
I didn't rest at home.

554
00:30:40,320 --> 00:30:41,440
I know.

555
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:46,000
But before you can find better ways,

556
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,560
it is better

557
00:30:48,160 --> 00:30:49,720
to stop and think.

558
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:51,880
If you dash blindly forward,

559
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,960
you may drift further

560
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:57,200
away from your goal.

561
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,920
[cellphone rings]

562
00:31:06,160 --> 00:31:07,160
Hello. Dad?

563
00:31:07,280 --> 00:31:08,880
[Xiangqian] Lu Xia, I had a car accident.

564
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,840
[Lu Xia] Car accident? Where are you?

565
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:12,960
-[Xiangqian] The municipal hospital.
-[Coach Qi gasps]

566
00:31:13,080 --> 00:31:14,240
Lu Xia.

567
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:17,160
[retreating footsteps]

568
00:31:18,720 --> 00:31:21,000
[panting]

569
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,240
[indistinct chatter]

570
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:24,200
[grunts]

571
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:25,120
[gasps]

572
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:27,480
[Xiangqian] Sorry, son.

573
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:28,960
I may not be able

574
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:31,200
to play tennis with you.

575
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:33,040
Can you forgive me?

576
00:31:33,520 --> 00:31:35,720
I saw you chatting happily
with your friends.

577
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:38,000
Why don't you have anything to say to me?

578
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,440
[splats]

579
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:42,160
[somber music]

580
00:31:44,640 --> 00:31:46,560
[Xiangqian] The crispy part
is the most delicious.

581
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:47,480
[soft chuckle]

582
00:31:49,560 --> 00:31:51,920
[panting]

583
00:31:52,360 --> 00:31:54,600
Dad. Dad.

584
00:32:00,360 --> 00:32:02,360
[dramatic music]

585
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:08,680
[panting]

586
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:11,400
[sizzling]

587
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:16,440
How about adding a cold dish?
It should be nutritious enough.

588
00:32:21,600 --> 00:32:23,360
[Xiangqian] Are you happy
when playing tennis?

589
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,280
[Lu Xia] Yes, I am.

590
00:32:25,560 --> 00:32:26,920
[Xiangqian] If it makes you happy,

591
00:32:27,000 --> 00:32:28,480
I will play with you forever.

592
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:30,360
[Lu Xia] Mm-hm.

593
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:33,480
[panting]

594
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,680
[dramatic music]

595
00:32:40,920 --> 00:32:41,920
[Coach Qi] Lu Xia.

596
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:43,600
Get inside.

597
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:51,000
-[doctor 2] He can leave the hospital now.
-[man 1] Okay, thank you.

598
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:55,800
[panting]

599
00:32:58,520 --> 00:33:01,400
[dramatic music]

600
00:33:02,280 --> 00:33:03,480
GOOD LUCK

601
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:09,960
-[panting]
-[distant chatter]

602
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:13,200
I'm looking for a victim
of a car accident.

603
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:14,280
Where is he now?

604
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:16,440
There is one in the therapy room.

605
00:33:16,520 --> 00:33:17,840
EMERGENCY ROOM

606
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,560
Dad!

607
00:33:20,800 --> 00:33:22,280
[man 2 groans]

608
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:24,360
[comical music]

609
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:30,040
When I was a tennis player,

610
00:33:30,880 --> 00:33:32,760
I had a tiny accident.

611
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:35,440
Then the doctors of all the
hospitals in Melbourne

612
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,040
lined up to see me.

613
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:39,440
Do you know how much insurance

614
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:41,560
the club bought for my leg?

615
00:33:43,080 --> 00:33:44,080
[Xiangqian] Look at this.

616
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:45,320
How much?

617
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,960
Fifty million dollars.

618
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:49,520
-[nurse 1] My goodness.
-Fifty million. It even scared me myself.

619
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:51,320
I was shocked, just as you're now.
[chuckles]

620
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,760
Stop it. Don't brag about yourself.

621
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:54,800
If you were Grand Slam Champion for tennis

622
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:56,480
I'd be a national table tennis player.

623
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:58,920
-I am telling the truth.
-[nurse 2] Get up first. Be quick.

624
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:02,000
Shouldn't I have a thorough inspection
and hospitalized for observation?

625
00:34:03,120 --> 00:34:04,400
[nurse 2] Stop it.

626
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:07,960
[wheelchair creaks]

627
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:09,159
You came.

628
00:34:11,320 --> 00:34:13,040
I thought you suffered a car accident?

629
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:16,440
When I went to buy some things for you,

630
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:18,480
I caught my finger in the door
and had a fracture

631
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:30,040
Didn't you say
you can't play tennis anymore?

632
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:31,480
[clears throat]

633
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,360
Fingers are connected with the heart.

634
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:35,400
It hurts when I move them.

635
00:34:45,600 --> 00:34:46,520
[Xiangqian stutters]

636
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:47,960
Brat.

637
00:34:49,120 --> 00:34:50,840
What are you doing? You are so cruel.

638
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:53,199
Just because I can't play tennis with you,

639
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,440
you want to abandon me.

640
00:34:56,600 --> 00:34:58,600
[somber music]

641
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:13,560
-[horn beeps]
-[siren wailing]

642
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:26,200
[somber music]

643
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,720
Luckily it is just the pinky.

644
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:46,640
[water ripples]

645
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:49,840
[sighs]

646
00:35:55,280 --> 00:35:57,560
So, don't you like fishing?

647
00:35:59,720 --> 00:36:01,200
It is not that I dislike it.

648
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:03,880
[Zhuo Zhi] Maybe I am not suitable for it.

649
00:36:04,560 --> 00:36:05,720
I thought you asked me

650
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:08,120
to play tennis on the weekend.

651
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,600
I thought

652
00:36:11,680 --> 00:36:13,760
you would like the concept,

653
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:16,560
"Freedom is always for the volunteers."

654
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:18,720
[soft chuckle]

655
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:22,600
If I'd really asked you to have a match,

656
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:23,960
would you have come?

657
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:25,800
Hmm.

658
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,760
Maybe.

659
00:36:26,840 --> 00:36:27,800
Zhuo Zhi.

660
00:36:28,520 --> 00:36:30,160
Since we were in 10th grade,

661
00:36:30,400 --> 00:36:32,960
you haven't played seriously
with me even once.

662
00:36:33,240 --> 00:36:35,440
Maybe it's because I'm afraid
I'll try to run away.

663
00:36:36,040 --> 00:36:36,880
[scoffs]

664
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:38,640
Why? Are you afraid of losing it to me?

665
00:36:39,200 --> 00:36:40,320
I am afraid of defeating you.

666
00:36:41,720 --> 00:36:43,400
I am afraid that everyone will ask me

667
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:46,280
to be the captain if I win.

668
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:49,200
After all, being a captain
is not an easy job. Just look at you now.

669
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,440
[sighs]

670
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:53,480
[soft chuckle]

671
00:36:55,360 --> 00:36:57,360
[tranquil music]

672
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,240
The bait is not taken.

673
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:10,280
I can't lose to you.

674
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:12,680
After all, I am not prepared

675
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,800
to lose.

676
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,880
[Zhuo Zhi] If I really lose to you,

677
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:18,080
I may cry in my room

678
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:19,760
for three days and nights.

679
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,240
[soft chuckle]

680
00:37:21,320 --> 00:37:22,240
Hmm.

681
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:24,840
[Siyang sighs]

682
00:37:26,720 --> 00:37:28,760
[tranquil music]

683
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:33,240
[sighs]

684
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:48,520
ZIWU ROAD STATION

685
00:37:48,760 --> 00:37:50,760
[Jian] The next bus will take
a long time to arrive.

686
00:37:51,520 --> 00:37:52,440
[soft chuckle]

687
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,160
Why are you here?

688
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,840
You've been staring
at the station board for ages.

689
00:37:58,240 --> 00:37:59,600
Here. My treat.

690
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:05,320
This is our homemade
sweet potato drinks. Try some.

691
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:14,000
[playful music]

692
00:38:16,600 --> 00:38:17,440
Ahh.

693
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:19,680
It is cool. Go on.

694
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,960
[Jian] Open it this way.

695
00:38:30,880 --> 00:38:32,400
[chuckles softly]

696
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:36,120
This reminds me of one of my seniors.

697
00:38:36,200 --> 00:38:38,200
[choir music]

698
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:41,680
[gurgles]

699
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,520
[soft chuckle]

700
00:38:53,440 --> 00:38:55,280
Why are you here?

701
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:58,360
Mr. Six said the air is fresh here.
It's nice for exercising.

702
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:00,280
Oh.

703
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:04,120
Eh. Do you have time?

704
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:05,960
How about having a match tomorrow?

705
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,720
I don't want to.

706
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:10,880
Don't worry. It won't be tennis.

707
00:39:11,720 --> 00:39:14,040
Come and find us tomorrow.
I will text you the location.

708
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,480
Do come.

709
00:39:19,200 --> 00:39:20,080
[Jian] Do come.

710
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:26,160
I didn't say yes.

711
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:37,320
[Jian] Lu Xia.

712
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:38,760
I knew you would come.

713
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:43,200
I just...

714
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:45,720
dropped by to...

715
00:39:46,320 --> 00:39:47,440
take a look.

716
00:39:47,760 --> 00:39:49,760
[uplifting music]

717
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:02,040
[uplifting music continues]

718
00:40:04,800 --> 00:40:06,320
[whooshes]

719
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:09,720
-[booming]
-[all grunting]

720
00:40:11,520 --> 00:40:12,480
Come on.

721
00:40:13,720 --> 00:40:15,320
Lu Xia, you should coordinate with me.

722
00:40:17,120 --> 00:40:18,760
Can't you play a ball game?

723
00:40:18,840 --> 00:40:20,240
Does this count as a ball game?

724
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:22,640
This game is called "Hearts Beating Hard."

725
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:25,360
You must pull the ropes to catch
the ball with the drums.

726
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,800
You lose if the ball falls on the ground.

727
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:30,160
Eh. The one who loses will be punished.

728
00:40:30,240 --> 00:40:31,880
-How?
-By getting drawings on his face.

729
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,080
I am leaving for training.

730
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:36,680
I'll lose if I play by myself.

731
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:41,040
Thank you for inviting me.

732
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,680
Are you just going away like this?

733
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:46,600
You may as well give up

734
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:49,120
if you can't handle something new
like this.

735
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,120
[Jian sighs]

736
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:15,440
We can't go on like this.
Our faces are almost full of pictures.

737
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:18,320
[funky music]

738
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:19,480
[grunts]

739
00:41:19,720 --> 00:41:22,000
You are not the kind to run away
from problems, are you?

740
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,440
I am not.

741
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,120
[sighs]

742
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,360
Sorry.

743
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:28,120
Our biggest problem

744
00:41:28,200 --> 00:41:29,600
is that our rhythms are different.

745
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:34,360
Eh. Then how about we set
a code for movement?

746
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:37,520
We don't have time to call out the code.

747
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:41,120
As long as we keep the
drum at this height,

748
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:42,320
there should be no problem.

749
00:41:47,640 --> 00:41:50,440
-[all grunting]
-[booming]

750
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,400
[whooshes]

751
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:56,840
[light music]

752
00:41:59,080 --> 00:42:00,560
-[both grunting]
-[booming]

753
00:42:05,480 --> 00:42:06,400
[gasps]

754
00:42:08,680 --> 00:42:10,680
[light music]

755
00:42:15,360 --> 00:42:16,360
[gasps]

756
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,240
[Jian] We succeeded.

757
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:21,640
Eh.

758
00:42:22,200 --> 00:42:25,160
Which group failed to catch the ball
just now?

759
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:28,800
They are the ones who drew the most
on our faces.

760
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:30,560
Lu Xia. Do you have a pen?

761
00:42:31,160 --> 00:42:32,280
[Coach Muyun grunts]

762
00:42:35,040 --> 00:42:36,240
It is time for revenge.

763
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:39,400
-[Coach Muyun chuckles]
-[Tian Ye] Run.

764
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:40,320
[Jian] Stop.

765
00:42:40,480 --> 00:42:42,000
[Tian Ye] Don't chase me.

766
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,880
Run.

767
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:45,520
[Zifeng] You should admit defeat.

768
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:47,880
[all laughing]

769
00:42:48,560 --> 00:42:49,600
[Tian Ye] Stop it.

770
00:42:50,760 --> 00:42:53,440
[all laughing]

771
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:59,400
[chuckles]

772
